metadata.name: Helix Records Genesis Pass #1
metadata.description:
Helix Records Genesis Pass. 

Helix Records is the new flagship electronic music label by veteran music executive Patrick Moxey. With Helix Records Moxey — who played a key role in the success of Avicii, Kygo, deadmau5 and David Guetta at Ultra Records — aims to make Web3 and NFTs a foundational part of the new venture.

The Helix Record Genesis drop consists of 3500 Genesis passes that give exclusive access to the Helix Records ecosystem. Genesis holders will become an integral part of Helix Records and have the chance to work with Patrick Moxey and his team to build Helix Records to become the biggest EDM label in the world and bring out the next superstars.
